Page_0:"Where's all the wine going? I asked for a few pints of fine red wine, and I don't get any. Seems like they're having problems with the wine supply into the town. Barely any have been seen for a few months, and they tell some stories about wolves and ghosts attacking them and then being robbed by mysterious people wearing cloaks. I wonder why the town guard doesn't do anything about it, they've been searching the forests around thoroughly but there's no wolves, ghosts or robbers. "




